---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="HeadlessUI Astro Playground">
	<main>
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">HeadlessUI for Astro</h1>
		<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
			Completely unstyled, fully accessible UI components for Astro.
		</p>

		<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800">Getting Started</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-blue-700">
					HeadlessUI Astro provides unstyled, accessible UI components that work seamlessly with Astro's partial hydration model.
				</p>
				<div class="mt-4">
					<pre class="bg-blue-900 text-blue-100 p-3 rounded text-sm overflow-auto">
npm install @headlessui-astro</pre>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-800">Components</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-purple-700">
					Explore the components by using the navigation on the left. All core components implemented:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 gap-x-4 text-purple-700">
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Menu (Dropdown)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Dialog (Modal)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Disclosure (Accordion)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Listbox (Select)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Combobox (Autocomplete)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Tabs
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Radio Group
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Switch (Toggle)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Popover
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800">Key Features</h2>
			<ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 gap-x-4">
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Fully accessible (WAI-ARIA compliant)
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Works with Astro's partial hydration
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Completely unstyled for maximum flexibility
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Interactive without full-page JavaScript
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Keyboard navigation support
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					TypeScript support
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-amber-800">Recent Updates</h2>
			<ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-amber-700">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-amber-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					<div>
						<strong class="font-medium">Advanced Component Combinations</strong>
						<p class="text-sm">New examples showing how to combine multiple components in complex patterns: Tabs inside Dialog and multi-component form layouts.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-amber-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					<div>
						<strong class="font-medium">Menu Component Enhancements</strong>
						<p class="text-sm">MenuSection, MenuHeading, and MenuSeparator components added to improve menu structure and accessibility.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-amber-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					<div>
						<strong class="font-medium">Full Component Set Implemented</strong>
						<p class="text-sm">All major components (Menu, Dialog, Disclosure, Listbox, Combobox, Tabs, Radio Group, Switch, Popover) now available.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-amber-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					<div>
						<strong class="font-medium">Hydration Guide Added</strong>
						<p class="text-sm">New documentation on using Astro's partial hydration with HeadlessUI components for optimal performance.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 bg-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800">Component Combinations</h2>
			<p class="mt-2 text-indigo-700">
				Explore how HeadlessUI components can be combined to create complex UI patterns:
			</p>
			<div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
				<a href="/combinations/tabs-in-dialog" class="block bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-indigo-700">Tabs in Dialog</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-indigo-600">See how to combine TabGroup and Dialog components for a tabbed modal interface</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/combinations/form" class="block bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-indigo-700">Complex Form</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-indigo-600">Multi-component form layout combining Switch, RadioGroup, and Disclosure components</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>